WEBVTT

00:11:28.934 --> 00:11:31.091
Utakapo sikia tena neno "saratani"

00:11:31.115 --> 00:11:33.541
Nataka uongeze kwenye hisia: matumaini.

00:11:34.303 --> 00:11:35.461
Subiri kwanza.

00:11:36.342 --> 00:11:39.915
Watafiti wa saratani duniani
wanafanya kazi kwa msisimko mkubwa

00:11:39.939 --> 00:11:41.095
kuushinda ugonjwa huu

00:11:41.119 --> 00:11:43.149
na maendeleo makubwa yanafanywa.

00:11:43.956 --> 00:11:45.924
Huu ni mwanzo wa mwisho wake.

00:11:46.380 --> 00:11:48.509
Tutashinda vita dhidi ya saratani.

00:11:48.861 --> 00:11:50.725
Na kwangu, hizi ni habari za kustaajabu

00:11:51.193 --> 00:11:52.360
Ahsanteni.

00:11:52.384 --> 00:11:56.905
(Makofi)